                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12157.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12157.htm">芥菜子Ê希望 [ KOÀ-CHHÀI CHÍ Ê HI-BŌNG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">芥菜子&Ecirc;希望
 
北部這坵園已經開不止久。所ǹg望&aacute;i...<a href="artical-12157.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
