          	  <a href="artical-src12158.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12158.htm">力間（海龍王） [ LE̍K-KAN (HÁI-LÊNG-ÔNG) ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">力間（海龍王）
 
　　佇一个熱天力間坐佇Ba-tek-海&ecirc;石磐，吟伊一生悲傷&ecirc;歌，用所gi&acirc; &ecirc;琴來彈。
　　青翠&ecirc;海湧，溢來溢去佇伊坐<span style="font-family: " lang=&quo...<a href="artical-12158.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
